message.body: Haha weve probably seen each other before
That's true. I am swamped this weekend but I would like to meet up and talk about music at some point
cool whats your weekday availability like?
Monday and Tuesday look good. Even Thursday.
Cool you work in the city?
No I work in NE Philly.
Well yes the city but not center city
Awesome. How long have u been singing?

Ummmm. Since I was 16 or so. Was in a band in high school. I have been taking it more seriously the past couple years. Have never done a serious performance but I want to start doing more singing publicly.
So what do you do with your music?
Nothing recorded yet??
Well I'm in a rap group. Were still kinda starting out. I make music videos also
Like professionally? No.
Welp we gotta change that
Haha. So you're looking for a female vocal to add to a song? Trying to remember your CL ad
Yep that's the plan
Very cool
Anywhere I can hear some of your stuff?
Yea u wanna see our latest video?
Absolutely. I'm at work now so I may not be able to watch it right away
What do u do for work?
I work with severely mental ill adults. My title is a psychiatric rehabilitation counselor. I'm a social worker by education. What about you?
Budget analyst for philly school district
Wowwwww. Tough job!! So your job depends on how much money the government will give you too
Awesome ill watch it ASAP
Yea shits been so bad for district. They are beyond broke
Did you go to college around here?
yup. temple. You?
St joes for undergrad.
U from philly originally?
Nope. Been here longest I've stayed put anywhere though so it's home. I went to middle school and high school in north jersey
How about you
I'm from norristown. Bout 30 min outside city. I'm not a fan of that suburb life though haha
Yup I know exactly where that is. An old roommate grew up there. Well, blue bell area
Yea that's close. You live with roommates now?
Yup. A girl and a guy now but the guys moving out and another girls moving in. You?
Yea I live with one roommate. Were cool but not like close friends or anything
Nice
Yea it works out well. Wish I could afford my own place though
Me tooooo. I'm hoping next summer ill move into a one bedroom
in Fairmount? Or doesn't matter?
Yeah probably. All my friends are around Fairmount and its a good commute to work
I think its best part of city
Wow bold statement!! My favorite part is Kelly drive so I guess it counts as Fairmount. I like to be near water.
What do u think is better?
Haha I guess I've never thought about a favorite part. I've lived in west (northwest) Philly, Manayunk, Germantown, and Fairmount. All have wonderful and not wonderful qualities
What's not wonderful about Fairmount? Jw what u think
Not close to train station
Can't stand that
Close to subway
Parking too but that's everywhere
U take train to work?
No but I have friends in Manayunk
And the bus there connects at ridge and that's a walk especially in heels if I go crazy and wear them
Lol I though train was close. I walk everywhere though dun really think anywhere downtown is far
I mean suburban station isn't THAT far. But I was used to a 10 min walk before I moved here so I was spoiled
Haha. I lived in manayunk for four years. I called it danayunk though
Danayunk??
yea. my name is Dan. I'm so clever right ;-)
Hahaha. I guess clever could describe it
Yea those were good times but I def like city more. So much more diversity down here
I completely agree
U grow up close to NYC?
Like 45-60 minutes.
So Ur a giants fan?!????
No but my family is.
Do u not enjoy sports?
Haha
Not football. I really tried. Went to some games. I can't stand it. Like baseball. Go phillies. And I play sports. Like playing more than watching
What do u play? U in pssc?
Yeah I am. Volleyball and kickball. Do you play?
No but I should I did kickball a few times in manayunk league
Yeah I did too. It's a lot of fun
I'm so competitive though. I had to be captain lol
Our captain is CRAZY competitive. I love it bc Althoigh I play for fun I like winning
For vball or kball?
Kickball.
U guys good?
Yeah. However we've choked 2 years in a row at playoffs
Same team each yr?;
Since I've been in Fairmount I played w the same team 2 seasons
Cool u guys must be good buddies by now then
Yeah. My good friend from grad school played and his brother is the captain. So I got recruited haha
Nice. My roommate plays pssc every season. Always tryna get me to join
It's a good time you should
Perhaps perhaps
So you're like a normal person? With Craigslist you never know
Lol yea have u had bad encounters?
Oh my god yea. Crazy story. When we meet up ill tell you
It's lengthy
Oh wow can't wait to hear lol
So is there 3 dudes in your group?
Yep. The video I sent u is my friend will "dubsac"...its his own video
So what do you do music wise
In the group or in my lifetime?
Both

I'm the video producer and rapper of the group. None of us produce any music. I have played saxophone a good portion of my life and I was also a music promoter foe awhile. Music has always been a part of my life in some facet it seems
I never really cared to rap honestly but my two best friends wanted me to with them
They both have been for years
But I am a big writer and I love hip hop so I was like sure why not. Its been fun and a good way to connect with them as we get older
Its not as easy to just chill with each other anymore so I kinda look at it as a fin hobby
I'm confused now bc I thought you were sending me some of your music and you sent me dub steps video so are you a part of that? Or did you produce the video? What do you need a singer for?
I'm making new songs. What do u mean
Yeah I was just showing u the last stuff we did
I need a singer for a chorus on new song
Dub step = lol
Dubsac***** hahaha
But who is we? Npire? Is that your group?
Yeah but the song I need u is just for me
Because your doing a solo project? Or are you just trying to kill me
Youre*
Yeah its a solo song. Lol why do u think I'm tryna kill u
Ever heard of the Craigslist killer?
well that's not me lol
Are u really nervous?
That's exactly what the Craigslist killer said. Even the "lol"
No not really. I mean I definitely wanna meet in a public place to make sure for the first meet up
yeah sure no prob
What if I'm a serial killer? Aren't YOU nervous?
Ur making me nervous lol
Haha I've never killed anyone. Don't worry
Stabbed but they didn't die so no big deal.
Well I dun wanna be stabbed either
I'm kidding.
R u home? I'm about to walk to liquor store on Fairmount if u wanna say hi and meet me
I am home yes. If you wanted to meet up at the corner of spring garden and 21. Or brandywine since you'll be walking south anyway
Yeah brandywine is fine. I'll let ya know when I leave
Alrighty
Leaving now
Ok so you stopping on your way back? Or should I go out now
im here now
O ok. Ill walk down the street
Nice to meet u. I look forward to meeting up again. Glad that neither of us look like murderers
Yes nice to meet you and that you didn't kill me. See you soon
